<p>Such an amazing variation of the classic and sometimes boring stool is of course subject to imitation, but Zanzibar and its heirs still remain a great piece for your modern decor. The extensive range of colors, the gas lift mechanism to easily adjust the height of the stool - everything is conceived with the smallest details firmly in mind.</p>

